-- Peter Volanakis to Retire as Corning's President, Chief Operating Officer
-- Steven Fromm
-- 2010-07-29T13:03:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/peter-volanakis-to-retire-as-corning-s-president-chief-operating-officer.html

          
          
             Corning Inc. said that Peter F.
Volanakis, president and chief operating officer, will retire on
or before Dec. 31.  
          
          


  


        